<p>	Q.  As far as the regional placement, I know that sometimes as far as date and things, maybe Stanford and Seattle seemed more logical, certainly, than Stanford and Norman? </p>
<p>	Q.  Could you just clarify the order of the No.  1s, was it Tennessee, Duke, Penn State and Texas? </p>
