<p>	Q.  Five or six years ago most of the top teams seemed to win their conference tournaments and it was pretty easy to pick or easier to pick the top seed.  How difficult was it to pick the top seeds, because they lost some of the team lost in their conference tournaments and there were more bubble teams this year.</p>
