<p>	Q.  Just curious if there was any particular consideration given against the top 50 opponents, an example, Vanderbilt being the 2 seed over Houston, or Notre Dame getting a 5 over Stanford's 6, would those teams be the only advantages  -- than higher-seeded teams had over the lower-seeded teams relative to the rest of the criteria, was there extra emphasis?</p>
